AGENTS1, BY ALAN SINGLETON (UNIVERSITY OF LEICESTER, PRIMARY COMMUNICATIONS
RESEARCH CENTRE). THE STUDY FOCUSED ON THE PART PLAYED BY AGENTS IN THE
